channel.title: Is Nganda back in Mexico?
channel.description: I've been wondering this for a couple of weeks now as the drug cartel matches up with Nganda, over some odd years ago there was this ancient blood cult that cherished a god named "Nganda", they took take tourists and do horrific things to them and eventually kill them, although 7 members are still alive as the rest got massacred by a guy named "Ed". So I was wondering if anyone knew if this is back again?
